  date         = {2025-01},
  abstract     = {The Twitter Moderation Research Consortium is a database of
                  network propaganda and influence operations that includes
                  115,474 unique Twitter accounts, millions of tweets, and over
                  one terabyte of media removed from the platform between 2017
                  and 2022. We probe this database using Google’s Vision API and
