                  timeline of volunteers using Facebook. We managed to convince
                  more than 2,000 volunteers to help our project and install our
                  tool. Then, we use a Convolution Neural Network (CNN) to
                  detect political Meta ads using word embeddings. To evaluate
                  our approach, we manually label a data collection of 10k ads
